Package: tonR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for operating the Talk of Norway dataset in R
Version: 0.1.1
Author@R: Martin Soyland <m.g.soyland@stv.uio.no> [aut, cre] and Emanuele Lapponi <emanuel@ifi.uio.no> [aut]
Maintainer: Martin Soyland <m.g.soyland@stv.uio.no>
Description: A package providing tools for reading and handling data in the Talk of Norway specification of 
    CoNLL data format. Features include making corpora, calculating readability scores, and producing 
    F-scores from classification experiments.
Depends: R (>= 3.1)
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/ltgoslo/src/R/tonR, https://github.com/ltgoslo
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: parallel
Suggests: dplyr,
    gsubfn,
    pbmcapply,
    tidytext
